newsitem.title: EU: OFFICIAL JOURNAL CONTENTS - OJ L 246 OF SEPTEMBER 27, 1996.
newsitem.headline: OFFICIAL JOURNAL CONTENTS - OJ L 246 OF SEPTEMBER 27, 1996.

text.p: (Note - contents are displayed in reverse order to that in the printed Journal)
COMMISSION DECISION of 29 May 1996 on aid from the Land of Lower Saxony to the company JAKO Jadekost GmbH & Co. KG (Only the German text is authentic) (Text with EEA relevance)

COMMISSION DECISION of 30 April 1996 enjoining the Kingdom of Spain to provide the necessary information in order to prove definitively that aid was granted under an existing aid scheme (Only the Spanish text is authentic) (Text with EEA relevance)
COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 1858/96 of 26 September 1996 establishing the standard import values for determining the entry price of certain fruit and vegetables

COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 1857/96 of 26 September 1996 amending Regulation (EEC) No 2219/92 laying down detailed rules for the application of the specific supply arrangements for Madeira relating to milk products regarding the amounts of aid

COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 1856/96 of 26 September 1996 amending Regulation (EC) No 2993/94 fixing the aid for the supply of milk products to the Canary Islands under the arrangements provided for in Articles 2 to 4 of Council Regulation (EEC) No 1601/92
COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 1855/96 of 26 September 1996 fixing the export refunds on milk and milk products

COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 1854/96 of 26 September 1996 establishing a list of reference methods to be applied for the analysis and quality evaluation of milk and milk products under the common market organization

COUNCIL REGULATION (EC) No 1853/96 of 24 September 1996 amending Regulation (EC) No 3088/95 laying down, for 1996, certain measures for the conservation and management of fishery resources applicable to vessels flying the flag of Poland

COUNCIL REGULATION (EC) No 1852/96 of 24 September 1996 amending Regulation (EC) No 3089/95 allocating, for 1996, certain catch quotas between Member States for vessels fishing in Polish waters END OF DOCUMENT.
